5000|$|<b>Steganography</b> Analyzer Artifact Scanner, or StegAlyzerAS, is {{computer}} forensics software made by Backbone Security's <b>Steganography</b> Analysis and Research Center. It {{is designed}} to extend the scope of traditional digital forensic examinations by allowing the examiner to scan suspect media or forensic images of suspect media for known artifacts of <b>steganography</b> applications.|$|E
